Name: Special Grant from the Pioneer Bureau
Description: From August 25th, 2025, at 5:00 to September 8th, 2025, at 05:00 (UTC-2), boss Loots will have a chance to drop an additional Module Gift Box. Opening the box grants a random excellent module.
Description2:
Upon witnessing your relentless efforts, Miss Valeria submitted a special request to the Pioneer Bureau on your behalf.
"Adventurer, consider this gift a token of my gratitude!"
